These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, country, jazz, trance
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, time-travel, crime, adventure
City: venice, rome, nizza, liverpool
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, lawyer, designer, nurse
 1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to nizza##3
 2. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the fan of trance##1
 3. the fan of blues is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person traveling to liverpool is the person watching time-travel movies##1
 5. the photographer is somewhere to the left of the designer##5
 6. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the lawyer##5
 7. the person traveling to rome is on the far left##1
 8. the designer is somewhere to the left of the person watching time-travel movies##5
 9. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
10. the person traveling to liverpool is somewhere between the photographer and the fan of blues##7
11. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
12. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere to the right of the nurse##5
13. the nurse is the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | country | jazz    | blues   |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | crime | time-travel | adventure |
| City           | rome       | nizza   | liverpool  | venice     |
| Job     | photographer      | designer   | nurse    | lawyer    |

