.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, february, september, july
House: tower, wooden, art-deco, gothic-revival
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, chinese, indonesian, italian
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, funk, ambient, house
 1. the fan of house is somewhere to the left of the fan of funk##5
 2. the indonesian is somewhere to the right of the italian##5
 3. the art-deco house is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5
 4. the fan of ambient is the australian##1
 5. the wooden house is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
 6. the chinese is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##5
 7. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere between the fan of funk and the australian##7
 8. the person who's birthday is in march is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the left of the fan of funk##5
10. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the right of the fan of folk##5
11. the chinese is the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3       |     4      |
| Birthday          | march   | september       | july    | february      |
| House   | tower | gothic-revival | wooden         | art-deco   |
| Nationality   | italian   | australian  | chinese       | indonesian |
| Music-Genre         | folk      | ambient  | house | funk |

