.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, designer, project-manager, social-worker
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, april, august, march
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, water, juice, sprite
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, salsa, punk, jazz
 1. the fan of jazz is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in august##5
 2. the fan of jazz is somewhere between the bartender and the person who's birthday is in august##7
 3. the designer is the person drinking water##1
 4. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the social-worker##3
 5. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
 6. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in november##5
 7. the project-manager is not the person who's birthday is in april##6
 8. the person who's birthday is in august is not the social-worker##6
 9. the bartender is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
10. the fan of jazz is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
11. the designer is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
12. the person drinking juice is the fan of punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3     |        4        |
| Job           | social-worker | bartender | designer | project-manager |
| Birthday   | november        | march    | april    | august    |
| Beverage   | fanta        | sprite   | water   | juice         |
| Music-Genre           | salsa          | d&b       | jazz   | punk           |

