4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, vegafina, blend, bongani
4 different pets are kept: lizard, goldfish, turtle, bird
4 different games are played: poker, canasta, chess, monopoly
 1. the person playing poker is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
 2. the owner of the bird is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 3. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
 4. the person drinking sprite is the person playing chess##1
 5. the baccarat-smoker is not the person playing poker##6
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
 7. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
 8. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the vegafina-smoker and the baccarat-smoker##7
 9. the owner of the goldfish is the person playing poker##1
10. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
11. the owner of the lizard is not the person playing poker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |        3        |      4       |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | soy-milk       | mirinda         | sprite       |
| Cigar         | baccarat     | bongani    | blend   | vegafina |
| Pet           | bird   | goldfish | turtle | lizard     |
| Game   | monopoly      | poker          | canasta           | chess |

