 8. the person who likes fuchsia is not the person playing scrabble##6
 9. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
10. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the french##1
11. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growslily##1
12. the person who likes black is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| Color         | ivory      | black   | fuchsia   | apricot       |
| Flower   | tulip | dahlia    | lily | iris       |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | colombian | french   | malaysian     |
| Game         | scrabble   | poker    | mah-jongg   | bridge |

