.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-18::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, colombian, italian, dutch
There 4 different types of food: apricot, artichoke, lemon, pear
The people have 4 different jobs:  paramedic, freelancer, social-worker, firefighter
4 different games are played: bridge, mah-jongg, monopoly, snooker
