 2. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the left of the person eating apricot##5
 3. the firefighter is between the person playing snooker and the person playing monopoly##2
 4. the paramedic is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 5. the person eating artichoke is not the person playing mah-jongg##6
 6. the firefighter is somewhere to the left of the person eating lemon##5
 7. the dutch is somewhere between the brazilian and the person eating pear##7
 8. the dutch is somewhere to the left of the person playing monopoly##5
 9. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the left of the freelancer##5
10. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the firefighter##1
11. the brazilian is the person eating lemon##1
12. the person eating lemon is not the person playing monopoly##6

