 2. the fan of electronic is between the person watching documentary movies and the person who's birthday is in august##2
 3. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
 4. the person playing backgammon is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the fan of funk is not the person who's birthday is in february##6
 7. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere between the person watching adventure movies and the person watching spy movies##7
 8. the fan of electronic is not the person watching spy movies##6
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is not the person watching adventure movies##6
10. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
11. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the fan of rock##1
12. the person watching documentary movies is not the person playing canasta##6
13. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
14. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
15. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3

