.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
House: tower, wooden, futuristic, gothic-revival
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, electronic, techno, punk
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, pony, rabbit, snake
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, horror, comedy, scientific
 1. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
 2. the fan of techno is the futuristic house##1
 3. the person watching horror movies is the owner of the snake##1
 4. the owner of the rabbit is between the gothic-revival house and the wooden house##2
 5. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the wooden house##5
 6. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the fan of techno and the tower house##7
 7. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the left of the fan of electronic##5
 8. the owner of the goldfish is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 9. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the left of the fan of trance##5
10. the owner of the pony is on the far right##1
11. the person watching comedy movies is in an even position##4
12. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the wooden house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| House   | gothic-revival      | futuristic     | wooden   | tower    |
| Music-Genre     | punk | techno   | electronic | trance |
| Pet     | snake        | rabbit     | goldfish  | pony      |
| Movie-Genre   | horror       | scientific | martial-arts   | comedy    |

 